		<para>
			&SHORT_PLATFORM_NAME; is an open source Java testing framework used to write and run automated tests for verifying SIP applications. 
			It extends the <ulink url="http://www.junit.org/">JUnit test framework</ulink> and adds SIP-specific assertions along with a high-level API for performing the SIP operations needed to interact with or invoke a test target. &PLATFORM_NAME; uses the <ulink url="http://code.google.com/p/jain-sip/">JAIN-SIP reference implementation</ulink> as its underlying SIP stack/engine.
		</para>
